Description: Typical range for industrial cleaning of reflective metals like cobalt to avoid thermal damage; starting at 100 W balances efficiency and safety. Max limited to prevent melting (cobalt MP ~1495°C). Source: IPG Photonics YLR series specs for metal cleaning.
